        </div>
        <div style="display:inline-block;background:rgba(37,211,102,0.1);color:#25D366;font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:600;padding:4px 12px;border-radius:9999px;margin-bottom:12px;">FASTEST RESPONSE</div>
